Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:36.44,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H744237&}究竟隱藏在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:41.64,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H744237&}我無數次地尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:47.54,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H744237&}閃耀的銀河之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:52.97,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H744237&}那僅屬於我的美麗光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.84,0:22:56.76,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H744237&}好了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.76,0:22:59.58,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H744237&}還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:02.37,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H744237&}好了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.37,0:23:13.63,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H744237&}等你到天長地久
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.29,0:23:21.85,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}再一次  無數次傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.85,0:23:27.43,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}無論如何不會改變的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.43,0:23:33.02,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}真正美麗的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.02,0:23:38.56,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}我從前便一直關注
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.56,0:23:41.32,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}唯一珍貴的事物  那便是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.32,0:23:46.73,ED-CN,,0,40,0,,{\an9\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}我與你的幸福吧
